  "title": "Snow halts bus and trolleybus traffic in capital",
  "text": "The sleet that turned into snow this morning in the capital has caused problems with public transport.\nAccording to a listener of the \"Horizont\" program, several trolleybuses and buses had difficulty moving on the so-called climb on \"Opalchenska\" street after \"Slivnitsa\" boulevard.\nAccording to him, the vehicles were climbing the icy street using emergency mode.\nDelays likely due to winter conditions.",
